Enum Configuration.Connection

    Configuration

    public static enum Configuration.Connection
extends java.lang.Enum<Configuration.Connection>
    The possible connections for data sources and targets. They are given by the command line argument --input and --output, or -i and -o. They are defining the 'mode of operation' of VeniceHub.
    • IIO - InstantIO
    • RSB - Robotics Service Bus
    • DISK - a file in the local file system
    • VP - a TCP socket (only as a source)
